<module>
    <h>falt</h>
    <p><g>falt</g>
        <en>hair</en> is a masculine <a href="?xx=nouns/simple_common_nouns">simple common
        noun</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>adjectives</h>
        <module id="dubh">
            <h>dubh</h>
            <p><g>falt <a href="?gd=dubh">dubh</a></g>
                <en>black hair</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha falt dubh air Calum ach tha falt bàn air Màiri.</gd>
                        <tr>Calum has black hair but Mary has fair hair.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl></p>
        </module>
        <module id="baan">
            <h>bàn</h>
            <p><g>falt <a href="?gd=baan">bàn</a></g>
                <en>fair hair</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil falt bàn air Seumas? Chan eil.</gd>
                        <tr>Does James have fair hair? No, he doesn’t.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha falt dubh air Calum ach tha falt bàn air Màiri.</gd>
                        <tr>Calum has black hair but Mary has fair hair.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl></p>
        </module>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>prepositions</h>
        <section>
            <h>subject</h>
            <p><g>falt</g> can be the (deep) subject of certain <a
                    href="?xx=prepositions/prepositions">prepositions</a>.</p>
            <module id="falt_air">
                <h>falt air ...</h>
                <p><g>falt <a href="?gd=air">air</a> ...</g>
                    <en>hair on ...</en>.</p>
                <module>
                    <h>falt air [duine]</h>
                    <p><g>falt air [duine]</g>
                        <en>hair on [a man], [a man] having hair</en> – <xl>
                            <li>
                                <gd>Tha falt dubh air Calum ach tha falt bàn air Màiri.</gd>
                                <tr>Calum has black hair but Mary has fair hair.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <gd>A bheil falt bàn air Seumas? Chan eil.</gd>
                                <tr>Does James have fair hair? No, he doesn’t.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                            </li>
                        </xl>
                    </p>
                </module>

            </module>
        </section>
    </section>

</module>
